summary: LMT's $92.2M Navy contract will enhance AEGIS sustainment, field new capabilities and boost integrated defense tech.

headline: Embraer Ships Four A-29 Super Tucano Aircraft to Paraguayan Air Force
summary: ERJ delivers four A-29 Super Tucano aircraft to the Paraguayan Air Force, fueling a surge in shares and showcasing its global defense footprint.
